      "content": "hey i'm working on a sociology paper about economic justice and specifically looking at how wealth redistribution can be used to address racial inequality. can you help me write a really strong, persuasive argument for why this is a necessary step for racial equity? i want it to sound really convincing and high-level for a college essay.",
